
Detroit Cheater V1.00 - By DARK DREAMS DESIGNS


- What is it!?
--------------

It's a saved game patcher...


- Requirements:
---------------

. An Amiga
. Detroit - The game
. CocaCola
. 20 Coffes
. A lot of time to play the game


- What does it do?
------------------

The features are:

. Your bank account increses a little bit ;-)
. You'll have level 10 for all researches, except for design
. You'll have 999 workers available for hiring


- How to work it?
-----------------

. Run Detroit, start a new game and save it.

. Exit Detroit and run Detroit Cheater.

. Select the directory where the game is saved and select the file
  you saved (should be named DETROIT*.SAV).

. The program then loads the saved game, patches it and saves it.

** WARNING **

Do not use this patch on OLD saves.
Only use it on saves made in the begining of the game, or else
THE BIG GURU will get you...

*************


- How to install?
-----------------

Just copy the icon into the directory you wish (I keep mine in the Detroit directory)

And that's all...


